{"tid":1080146,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［恥笑］廣電總局受群眾壓力 限古令即時解封","createTime":"2019-03-27T11:44:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-27T13:08:50.000Z","uid":54733,"like":17,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"e256cd7848106e1de11d07bf6215afa96b1ba532","tid":1080146,"uid":54733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-27T11:44:40.000Z","msg":"【話變就變】廣電總局受群眾壓力 限古令即時解封<br />\n<br />\n大陸廣電總局上周下達「限古令」，只要是武俠、玄幻、歷史、神話、穿越、宮鬥的古裝戲禁播到6月，但官方未想到業內和觀眾反應如此大，網民都鬧爆（新聞連結： <a href=\"https://bit.ly/2THJFA4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2THJFA4&d=5mmA4sQKuQaI7%2FjJJ4WTl%2FvW7D1Q%2FvztR01HWodNoCE%3D&h=a9f1dfb5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2THJFA4</a> ）。日前廣電總局網絡司分別召集3家平台，當3家平台簽下保證書後，古裝劇4月可逐步上線，換言之，古裝劇解封了。<br />\n<br />\n保證書內提到解封的條件，包括每月15日前網路平台要通過廣電總局交代每月上線的古裝劇列表，還有現實題材要佔年度60%、以及未拿到上線許可的古裝劇，一律不能提前排播或宣傳，而參與會議的3家最大平台都寫了保證書。所以之前被禁的《新白娘子傳奇》，今日公佈重新定檔下月3日於愛奇藝播出。首度拍攝電視劇的章子怡與楊祐寧演出的《帝凰業》也重新安排播映。"},{"pid":"3a9922a2428a28fa6944ecf1d5e8d1fe94d63e59","tid":1080146,"uid":54733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-27T11:45:00.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20190327/59417673\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190327%2F59417673&d=5mmA4sQKuQaI7%2FjJJ4WTl%2FvW7D1Q%2FvztR01HWodNoCE%3D&h=76b36ba1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190327%2F59417673&h=c335bb6b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20190327/59417673</a>"},{"pid":"53f7582699434abb24c336d107801f1677c7b8c9","tid":1080146,"uid":169994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-27T11:45:53.000Z","msg":"彈出彈入，你吹得我漲咩"},{"pid":"47747913891d57ccd1d44aeca7c8b0add5b46f70","tid":1080146,"uid":15830,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,